- login to AWS
- launch one Instance (Ubuntu)
- login to instance 
- add inbound rule : http, tcp, ssh, 
- access instance using putty, gitbash

- sudo apt-update
- install/update python
- install nginex , curl 
 
- clone your github project to particular directry
- create virtual env. 
- activate env
- install all requirements 

- python manage.py runserver

if we get any error in code ,we have to again start our sever 
python manage.py runserver



